data.description: One of a kind property between Manhattan and Wamego.  This beautiful walkout ranch home features all the amenities you want, and then some.  Five large bedrooms, three beautiful bathrooms a fantastic theater room and an amazing work out room. And that's not all! How about a huge pantry, large laundry room and a very special safe room you have to see to believe.  A mammoth three car garage with plenty of storage is only the beginning.  There is a 30'x50' metal building with 14' tall drive through doors to store you RV on site.  Now, how about that covered deck to relax on and watch the sunset every evening?  40'x10' big enough, how about the same size patio below leading to an above ground pool to enjoy all summer long? We haven't even talked about the kitchen yet!  Beautiful custom cabinets with solid surface tops and tile backsplash with an island just waiting for your next get together with family and friends. Low Pott. county taxes and no specials makes this home the Best Buy ever!
